msgid "In general, more CPU cores available in the cloud allow for more work to be done in *parallel* and reduce time to solution (a CPU-bound program). Parallel computing is where multiple CPU cores can be used simultaneously to solve a computational problem, e.g. running the same processing task on several different datasets."
